title: Gov't: Nana Addo's Interview Was Not 'Relevant' To Gov't For Citi FM's Signal To Be Jammed
text: Deputy Communications Minister , Felix Kwakye Ofosu, has retorted to claims by NPP ’s Dr. Matthew Opoku Prempeh aka Napo that government deliberately jammed Accra based Citi FM frequency signal during a studio interview with NPP’s flagbearer,
